OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine at
OL,7,Ffirst, but gradually clouding over
OL,8,Ffrom the west. Cloud and rain will
OL,9,Fspread east to all parts overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FRain will soon clear east
OL,12,Fthen sunny spells and showers. Drier
OL,13,Ffor a time in the afternoon before
OL,14,Ffurther showers later, heavy at times.
OL,15,FCool and blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
