OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday and
OL,7,FThursday with scattered heavy showers.
OL,8,FChance of overnight frost. Windy
OL,9,Faround the coast on Thursday. Mostly
OL,10,Fdry on Friday but a few early showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
